text: Harry Butterworth (22 November 1867 - 30 November 1954) was a British fencer. He competed in the individual and team sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1867 births Category:1954 deaths Category:British male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Great Britain Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
